.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, salsa, country, electronic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, march, february
1. the fan funk is on the left of the fan country##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
4. the fan electronic is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | country | electronic  | salsa |
| Birthday      | march | may  | february | september    |

