.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, poppy, sunflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, emerald, coral
1. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsazalea is the person who likes azure##1
5. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsazalea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Flower   | azalea     | poppy           | tulip | sunflower  |
| Color         | azure | coral | light-blue   | emerald |

