.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, may, september
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, cricket, soccer
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | september   | july | january | may      |
| Sport     | cricket | skateboarding    | lacrosse  | soccer |

