.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cape-cod, palace
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, amber, azure, green
1. the person who likes orange is the townhouse house##1
2. the person who likes amber is between the cape-cod house and the person who likes azure##2
3. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| House       | farmhouse | palace | cape-cod     | townhouse   |
| Color   | azure   | amber     | green | orange |

