.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
City: new-york, paris, prague, hannover
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, tea, milk
1. the person traveling to prague is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person traveling to new-york##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| City         | paris | prague | new-york | hannover |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | milk       | lemonade    | tea         |

