.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, photography, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, punk, folk
1. the fan house is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the fan punk is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the fan punk is on the right of the fan house##1
5. the fan house is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the fan folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby    | fishing   | photography      | traveling   | collecting  |
| Music-Genre   | folk | house | punk | funk |

