4. the person who growstennispy is the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsdahlia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
