.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall, oliveros, havana
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, fanta, almond-milk
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is between the person drinking almond-milk and the cain-smoker##2
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar         | cain      | havana | pall-mall  | oliveros |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta  | almond-milk | juice    |

