2. the gothic-revival house is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing billiard is between the person playing snooker and the victorian house##2
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | gothic-revival | victorian | craftsman | palace |
| Game           | bridge  | mah-jongg  | billiard | snooker      |

