The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, lacrosse, handball
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
3. the pakistani is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the japanese##2
4. the thai is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality       | thai | pakistani | japanese | indonesian |
| Sport   | water-polo    | parkour  | handball    | lacrosse       |

