.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, techno, electronic
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, fuchsia, coral, emerald
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the fan electronic is the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes emerald is between the fan funk and the fan techno##2
5. the fan techno is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | funk   | hip-hop | techno |
| Color         | aquamarine | fuchsia | emerald     | coral    |

