.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, epic, musical
House: modern, farmhouse, wooden, futuristic
1. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the person watching action movies is between the modern house and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | musical     | action | adventure |
| House     | farmhouse | futuristic | wooden       | modern     |

 